&lt;h1&gt;Sonam’s Dilemma - A Gift for Few or a Chance for All&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;section id="bonus-question-1-point" class="level6"&gt;
&lt;h6 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="bonus-question-1-point"&gt;Bonus Question : 1 point&lt;/h6&gt;
