&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;section id="instructions" class="level3"&gt;
&lt;h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="instructions"&gt;Instructions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Due Date : July 7, Friday, 5 pm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Submit your answer at D2 &gt; Quiz &gt; “Sonam’s Dilemma : a gift for few or a chance for all”&lt;/li&gt;
